<div class="thumb tleft">
<div class="thumbinner" style="width:162px;"><a href="/wiki/File:YinchuanMosque.jpg" class="image" title="Taizi Mosque in Yinchuan."><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/d/d7/YinchuanMosque.jpg/160px-YinchuanMosque.jpg" width="160" height="130" border="0" class="thumbimage" /></a>
<div class="thumbcaption">
<div class="magnify"><a href="/wiki/File:YinchuanMosque.jpg" class="internal" title="Enlarge"><img src="/skins-1.5/common/images/magnify-clip.png" width="15" height="11" alt="" /></a></div>
Taizi Mosque in <a href="/wiki/Yinchuan" title="Yinchuan">Yinchuan</a>.</div>
